race.comment: LAND BANK (7) has been right there in both runs since rejoining the Gollan yard and looks to be working up to another victory. Jones sticks in the irons following the past couple of efforts and should be right there at the business end. CREATIVITY MISS (1) has placed three of four around this circuit and will be at peak fitness for this. Ready to find winning form. NICCONIUM (9) finally got the maiden out of the way over this course and distance last time out and may have turned the corner now. Top-three contender. SUMMIT (12) draws low for Maloney and must be respected out of the Waller yard. In the mix.
